      <li><a href="/reading/real-analysis/lebl-05/">∞ Real Analysis Ch.5</a> — the derivative defined rigorously with epsilon-delta</li>
      <li><a href="/reading/physics/crowell-01/">⚛ Physics Ch.1</a> — derivatives as rates of change in mechanics</li>
      <li><a href="/reading/machine-learning/ml-03/">🤖 ML Ch.3</a> — gradient descent is iterative derivative-following</li>
    </ul>
    </Neighbors>

    <PrevNext prev={{ href: "/reading/calculus/calc-03/", label: "Limits and Continuity" }} next={{ href: "/reading/calculus/calc-05/", label: "Derivative Rules · 5 of 15" }} />

  </main>
</Layout>
